#. <section class="sutta" id="sn44.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn44.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 44"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 44"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn44.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Abyākatavagga"
msgstr "1. The Undeclared Points"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Vacchagottasutta → bhandhasuttaṃ (bj) | vaccho (or bhandhaṃ) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn44.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Vacchagottasutta"
msgstr "8. With Vacchagotta"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn44.8:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho vacchagotto paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the wanderer Vacchagotta went up to the Buddha and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

msgctxt "sn44.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho vacchagotto paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side, and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn44.8:1.3"
msgid "“kiṃ nu kho, bho gotama, sassato loko”ti?"
msgstr "“Master Gotama, is this right: ‘the world is eternal’?”"

msgctxt "sn44.8:1.4"
msgid "“Abyākataṃ kho etaṃ, vaccha, mayā: ‘sassato loko’ti … pe …."
msgstr "“This has not been declared by me, Vaccha.” …"

msgctxt "sn44.8:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Kiṃ pana, bho gotama, ‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Then is this right: ‘a Realized One neither exists nor doesn’t exist after "
"death’?”"

msgctxt "sn44.8:1.6"
msgid "“Etampi kho, vaccha, abyākataṃ mayā:"
msgstr "“This too has not been declared by me.”"

msgctxt "sn44.8:1.7"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn44.8:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu, ko paccayo, yena aññatitthiyānaṃ "
"paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhānaṃ evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"“What’s the cause, Master Gotama, what’s the reason why the wanderers who "
"follow other paths answer these questions when asked?"

msgctxt "sn44.8:2.2"
msgid "‘sassato loko’ti vā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:2.3"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti vā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ko pana, bho gotama, hetu, ko paccayo, yena bhoto gotamassa evaṃ puṭṭhassa "
"na evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""
"And what’s the cause, what’s the reason why Master Gotama doesn’t answer "
"these questions when asked?”"

msgctxt "sn44.8:2.5"
msgid "‘sassato loko’tipi … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:2.6"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipī”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.396"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn44.8:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatitthiyā kho, vaccha, paribbājakā rūpaṃ attato samanupassanti, "
"rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā rūpaṃ, rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Vaccha, the wanderers who follow other paths regard form as self, self as "
"having form, form in self, or self in form."

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.2"
msgid "Vedanaṃ attato samanupassanti … pe …"
msgstr "They regard feeling …"

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.3"
msgid "saññaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.4"
msgid "saṅkhāre … pe …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.5"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassanti, viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā "
"viññāṇaṃ, viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"consciousness as self, self as having consciousness, consciousness in self, "
"or self in consciousness."

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.6"
msgid ""
"Tasmā aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhānaṃ evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "That’s why they answer these questions when asked."

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.7"
msgid "‘sassato loko’ti vā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.8"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.9"
msgid ""
"Tathāgato ca kho, vaccha, arahaṃ sammāsambuddho na rūpaṃ attato "
"samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā rūpaṃ, na rūpasmiṃ vā "
"attānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The Realized One doesn’t regard form as self, self as having form, form in "
"self, or self in form."

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.10"
msgid "Na vedanaṃ attato samanupassati … pe …"
msgstr "He doesn’t regard feeling …"

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.11"
msgid "na saññaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.12"
msgid "na saṅkhāre … pe …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.13"
msgid ""
"na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, na viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā "
"viññāṇaṃ, na viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"consciousness as self, self as having consciousness, consciousness in self, "
"or self in consciousness."

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.14"
msgid "Tasmā tathāgatassa evaṃ puṭṭhassa na evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "That’s why he doesn’t answer these questions when asked.”"

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.15"
msgid "‘sassato loko’tipi … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:3.16"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn44.8:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho vacchagotto paribbājako uṭṭhāyāsanā yenāyasmā mahāmoggallāno "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā mahāmoggallānena saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the wanderer Vacchagotta got up from his seat and went to Venerable "
"Mahāmoggallāna, and exchanged greetings with him."

msgctxt "sn44.8:4.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho vacchagotto paribbājako āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side. He asked Mahāmoggallāna the same questions, and received the same "
"answers. Then he said:"

msgctxt "sn44.8:4.3"
msgid "“kiṃ nu kho, bho moggallāna, sassato loko”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:4.4"
msgid "“Abyākataṃ kho etaṃ, vaccha, bhagavatā: ‘sassato loko’ti … pe …."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:4.5"
msgid ""
"“Kiṃ pana, bho moggallāna, ‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:4.6"
msgid "“Etampi kho, vaccha, abyākataṃ bhagavatā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:4.7"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn44.8:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Ko nu kho, bho moggallāna, hetu, ko paccayo, yena aññatitthiyānaṃ "
"paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhānaṃ evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:5.2"
msgid "‘sassato loko’ti vā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:5.3"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti vā?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:5.4"
msgid ""
"Ko pana, bho moggallāna, hetu, ko paccayo yena samaṇassa gotamassa evaṃ "
"puṭṭhassa na evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:5.5"
msgid "‘sassato loko’tipi … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:5.6"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipī”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.397"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn44.8:6.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatitthiyā kho, vaccha, paribbājakā rūpaṃ attato samanupassanti, "
"rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā rūpaṃ, rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.2"
msgid "Vedanaṃ attato samanupassanti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.3"
msgid "saññaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.4"
msgid "saṅkhāre … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.5"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassanti, viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā "
"viññāṇaṃ, viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.6"
msgid ""
"Tasmā aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhānaṃ evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.7"
msgid "‘sassato loko’ti vā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.8"
msgid "‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’ti vā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.9"
msgid ""
"Tathāgato ca kho, vaccha, arahaṃ sammāsambuddho na rūpaṃ attato "
"samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā rūpaṃ, na rūpasmiṃ vā "
"attānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.10"
msgid "Na vedanaṃ attato samanupassati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.11"
msgid "na saññaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.12"
msgid "na saṅkhāre … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.13"
msgid ""
"na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, na viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā "
"viññāṇaṃ, na viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.14"
msgid "Tasmā tathāgatassa evaṃ puṭṭhassa na evaṃ veyyākaraṇaṃ hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn44.8:6.15"
msgid ""
"‘sassato loko’tipi, ‘asassato loko’tipi, ‘antavā loko’tipi, ‘anantavā loko’"
"tipi, ‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’tipi, ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’tipi, ‘hoti "
"tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi, ‘na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi, ‘hoti ca "
"na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’tipi, ‘neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato "
"paraṃ maraṇā’tipī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn44.8:7.1"
msgid "“Acchariyaṃ, bho moggallāna, abbhutaṃ, bho moggallāna."
msgstr "“It’s incredible, Master Moggallāna, it’s amazing."

msgctxt "sn44.8:7.2"
msgid ""
"Yatra hi nāma satthu ca sāvakassa ca atthena attho byañjanena byañjanaṃ "
"saṃsandissati, samessati, na virodhayissati, yadidaṃ aggapadasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"How the meaning and the phrasing of the teacher and the disciple fit "
"together and agree without contradiction when it comes to the chief matter!"

msgctxt "sn44.8:7.3"
msgid ""
"Idānāhaṃ, bho moggallāna, samaṇaṃ gotamaṃ upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ apucchiṃ."
msgstr "Just now I went to the ascetic Gotama and asked him about this matter."

msgctxt "sn44.8:7.4"
msgid ""
"Samaṇopi me gotamo etehi padehi etehi byañjanehi etamatthaṃ byākāsi, "
"seyyathāpi bhavaṃ moggallāno."
msgstr ""
"And he explained it to me with these words and phrases, just like Master "
"Moggallāna."

msgctxt "sn44.8:7.5"
msgid "Acchariyaṃ, bho moggallāna, abbhutaṃ, bho moggallāna."
msgstr "It’s incredible, Master Moggallāna, it’s amazing!"

msgctxt "sn44.8:7.6"
msgid ""
"Yatra hi nāma satthu ca sāvakassa ca atthena attho byañjanena byañjanaṃ "
"saṃsandissati samessati na virodhayissati, yadidaṃ aggapadasmin”ti."
msgstr ""
"How the meaning and the phrasing of the teacher and the disciple fit "
"together and agree without contradiction when it comes to the chief matter!”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn44.8:7.7"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
